{"tid":1065044,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"人到中年, 生活在香港無希望無將來, 如果可以, 希望能望過越南打工生活","createTime":"2019-03-17T03:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T07:59:57.000Z","uid":76310,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dc35a2f5f4b29be5361e2ef0a67433a955cff097","tid":1065044,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"人到中年, 生活在香港無希望無將來, 如果可以, 希望能望過越南打工生活<br />\n希望不久將來朋友能夠介紹我到越南生活<br />\n在香港生活像如狗, 番工不時塞車, 番工環境又差, 香港天氣又濕又熱, 周圍都時人迫迫迫, 工作壓力大好多獲氣, 沒有將來, 沒有希望, 常常不開心, 發現自己常常黑面, 笑不出來, 看見一堆狗官貪官出賣香港自己圖利, 香港將來沒有希望<br />\n不貪心, 希望能夠將來到越南工作, 在當地收香港3萬人工(以當地購買力來計, 即是香港購買力十多萬咁上下), 生活立即改善, 不是人上人, 也至少是中產生活, 可以住大屋, 渣靚車, 小美女, 食好住好<br />\n有時會想, 天天為什麼不自殺, 因為至少呢個係我惟一的希望<br />\n六合彩是香港人的希望, 但我覺得根本不實際, 因為機會率和0沒有分別"},{"pid":"ec69d4fc78e09f6c15774950d82b79b17290a03a","tid":1065044,"uid":76310,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"今天看到這個片, 越南夜生活<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RlcNhhQm0wo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRlcNhhQm0wo&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=38999037\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RlcNhhQm0wo</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bc316a872a381d672ec032f8ffe9980bae62b0","tid":1065044,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-vELC2U3Xxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-vELC2U3Xxw&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=31909f8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-vELC2U3Xxw</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"